<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where after consultations referred to in Article 3, it is apparent to the Commission that there is sufficient evidence to justify the initiation of an investigation, the Commission shall: </inglise>
