<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The provisions of this Title shall not preclude the use, at any time, of surveillance measures in accordance with Articles 11 to 15 or provisional safeguard measures in accordance with Articles 16, 17 and 18. </inglise>
