<inglise> Article 9 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 9 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Information received pursuant to this Regulation shall be used only for the purpose for which it was requested. </inglise>
