<inglise> Article 10 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 10 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Examination of the trend of imports, of the conditions in which they take place and of serious injury or threat of serious injury to Community producers resulting from such imports shall cover in particular the following factors: </inglise>
