<inglise> In this regard account may be taken of factors such as: </inglise>
<eesti> Sellega seoses v&otilde;ib arvesse v&otilde;tta j&auml;rgmisi tegureid: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) the rate of increase of the exports to the Community; </inglise>
