<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Until 31 December 1995, Spain and Portugal may maintain the quantitative restrictions on agricultural products referred to in Articles 77, 81, 244, 249 and 280 of the Act of Accession. </inglise>
